1. Intall python pip

$ sudo su 
$ apt-get update
$ apt-get -y install python-pip
$ pip --help
$ pip -V
$ python -m pip install --upgrade pip setuptools wheel

2. Install PyStemmer 

$ pip install PyStemmer

3. Install nltk (natural language toolkit)

$ pip install nltk

4. Install nltk.punkt, nltk.stopwords


$ python 
>> import nltk 
>> nltk.download('punkt')
>> nltk.download('stopwords')
